OL,3,CHomeless woman sleeping rough in tent
OL,4,Cin Reading dies
OL,6,FA woman who was sleeping rough in a
OL,7,Ftent in Reading has died.
OL,9,FGenevieve Curwen who was in her
OL,10,Ffifties - was taken to hospital on 19
OL,11,FFebruary after the emergency services
OL,12,Fresponded to a 'fear for welfare
OL,13,Fincident' on Broad Street.
OL,15,FFlowers been left where her tent was.
OL,17,FReading Borough Council says its
OL,18,Fthoughts are with her family at this
OL,19,Ftime, and all of those who knew her.
