OL,3,CHomeless woman sleeping rough in tent
OL,4,Cin Reading dies
OL,6,FThey say she was well known to the St
OL,7,FMungo's outreach service in the town
OL,8,Fbut that sadly a wide range of
OL,9,Faccommodation options that were
OL,10,Foffered to her were not taken up.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the council said:
OL,13,F"The Council and its partners were
OL,14,Fdeeply saddened to learn that the
OL,15,Fwoman concerned has passed away.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with her family at
OL,18,Fthis time, and all of those who knew
OL,19,Fher.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
