PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772374274
OL,3,CHomeless woman sleeping rough in tent
OL,4,Cin Reading dies
OL,6,F"She was well known to the St Mungo's
OL,7,Foutreach service in Reading, who are
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the Council to support
OL,9,Fpeople sleeping rough locally.
OL,11,F"A wide range of accommodation options
OL,12,Fwere offered over a sustained period
OL,13,Fof time, but these were sadly not
OL,14,Ftaken up.
OL,16,F"Alongside this, St Mungo's outreach
OL,17,Fteam also offered repeated on-street
OL,18,Fengagement, welfarefocused support
OL,19,Fand links to wider health and
OL,20,Fspecialist services.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
