PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772374274
OL,3,CHomeless woman sleeping rough in tent
OL,4,Cin Reading dies
OL,6,F"Recent offers of accommodation were
OL,7,Fadditionally declined as part of the
OL,8,FCouncil's Severe Weather Emergency
OL,9,FProtocol (SWEP), which was active
OL,10,Fbetween February 13 -20, alongside
OL,11,Fother support offered by the Council's
OL,12,Fadult social care team, and similarly
OL,13,Ffrom NHS health outreach teams." .
